## ğŸ› ï¸ Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/Dibyajyotid/StayFinder.git

cd stayfinder

cd client
npm install

cd..

cd backend
npm install

then make an .env file in the backend with these data and provide own data

JWT_SECRET =
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME =
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY =
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET =
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY =
CLIENT_URL=
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET =  
MONGO_URI =

